organizations: College of Charleston on Pinehurst Country Club
title: @OspreyWGolf Finishes 8th at Pinehurst Challenge
text: Mary Dawson and a record setting tournament team total, the North Florida women's golf team earned an eighth-place finish Tuesday at the Pinehurst Challenge hosted by the College of Charleston on Pinehurst Country Club's No. 1 Course (par 72 / 5,949 yards).The Ospreys shot a final round 300 en route to posting a 54-hole total of 877 (+13), eclipsing the program record of 880 set earlier this season in the JU Classic. Dawson finished tied for seventh in the medalist competition, shooting a three-round 4-under 212 that included a second consecutive even-par 72 in the final round.Dawson was joined in the Top 20 individuals by junior teammate
